'''金巴沃德县'''（[[印地语|印地语]]：चमोली ज़िला）是[[印度|印度]]北部[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]的一个县，县治位于金巴沃德，该县下辖5个乡：Barakot乡、金巴沃德乡、Lohaghat乡、 帕蒂乡及 Purnagiri乡。该县属于[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]下辖的两个专区之一的[[库马盎专区|库马盎专区]]，东与[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]][[馬哈卡利專區|馬哈卡利專區]]毗邻,北临[[比托拉格尔县|比托拉格尔县]]，南临[[乌但辛那加县|乌但辛那加县]]，西临[[奈尼塔尔县|奈尼塔尔县]]，西北临[[阿尔莫拉县|阿尔莫拉县]]。

该县是[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]13个县中人口第二少的县（最少的县是[[鲁德勒布勒亚格县|鲁德勒布勒亚格县]]）<ref name="districtcensus">{{cite web | url = http://www.census2011.co.in/district.php | title = District Census 2011 | accessdate = 2011-09-30 | year = 2011 | publisher = Census2011.co.in | archive-date = 2011-06-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611224943/http://www.census2011.co.in/district.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==人文==
截至[[2011年印度人口普查|2011年印度人口普查]]，金巴沃德县有人口259,315,<ref name="districtcensus"/>，与[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]]大致相等<ref name="cia">{{cite web | author = US Directorate of Intelligence | title = Country Comparison:Population | url = https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2119rank.html | accessdate = 2011-10-01 | quote = Vanuatu 224,564 July 2011 est. | archive-date = 2011-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927165947/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2119rank.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。 人口密度为 每平方公里147人<ref name=districtcensus/>。人口增长率(2001-2011)为15.49%.<ref name=districtcensus/> ，男女性别比为0.98(1000:981)<ref name=districtcensus/>,识字率80.73%<ref name=districtcensus/>。 

金巴沃德县有印度教徒216,646（96.5％），穆斯林6,642（3.0％），基督徒626（0.3％）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://india.gov.in/knowindia/districts/andhra1.php?stateid=UA | title = Uttarakhand - Districts of India: Know India | publisher = National Portal of India | accessdate = 2009-04-04 | archive-date = 2009-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090219225233/http://india.gov.in/knowindia/districts/andhra1.php?stateid=UA | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==经济==
金巴沃德县是印度640个县中最不发达的250个县之一<ref name=brgf/> ，也是[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]实施扶贫计划（the Backward Regions Grant Fund Programme ；BRGF）的3个县之一<ref name=brgf>{{cite web|author=Ministry of Panchayati Raj|date=September 8, 2009|title=A Note on the Backward Regions Grant Fund Programme|publisher=National Institute of Rural Development|url=http://www.nird.org.in/brgf/doc/brgf_BackgroundNote.pdf|accessdate=September 27, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405033402/http://www.nird.org.in/brgf/doc/brgf_BackgroundNote.pdf|archivedate=2012-04-05}}</ref>。

